\id 2TH - Tuivang Holy Bible
\h 2 THESSALONIKA
\toc1 2 Thessalonika
\toc2 2 Thessalonika
\toc3 2 Thess
\mt1 2 THESSALONIKA
\c 1
\s1 Zeelnaak Awi
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Cei 17.1.\x*Paul, Sila ingkaw Timote ing Ningmih a Pa Khawsa ingkaw Bawipa Jesu Khrih awh ak awm Thesalonika khaw awhkaw thlangboel a venawh:
\v 2 Pa Khawsa ingkaw Bawipa Jesu Khrih a venawh kaw qeennaak ingkaw ngaihqepnaak awm seh.
\s1 Khawsa A Laitlyknaak Ingkaw Kyihcahnaak
\p 
\v 3 Koeinaakhqi, nangmih ak cangnaak ing taai hqui khqoet khqoet nawh, nangmih pynoet ingkaw pynoet naming lungqunaak awm a taai hqui a dawngawh nangmih awh ce Khawsa venawh zeelawi ka mik kqawn poepa aham awm nawh, kqawn aham awm tyng qoe hy.
\p 
\v 4 Cedawngawh, nangmih ang yhnaak, kyinaak ingkaw sykzoeknaak soepkep anglakawh cangnaak nami taak ce Khawsa thlangboel khqi anglakawh ning cawngcah pyi khqi unyng.
\v 5 Vemyihkhqi boeih awh ve Khawsa ak awitlyknaak taw thym hy tive dang hy. Cedawngawh nangmih taw Khawsa qam thlangkhqi na noet sih na awm kawm uk ti, ce aham ni nangmih ing nami khuikha hy.
\v 6 Khawsa taw dyng hy: Nangmih kyinaak anik pe thlangkhqi ce anih ing kyinaak pe tlaih kawmsaw,
\v 7 nangmih kyinaak ak hukhqi venawh hawihkhangnaak ce pe kaw, kaimih awm ni pek khqi lawt kaw. Bawipa Jesu Khrih ce khawk khan nakawng maikqawng ing khan ceityih thaawmnaak ing ang dang law awh vemyihkhqi ve awm kaw.
\v 8 Khawsa amak simkhqi ingkaw ni Bawipa Jesu Khrih ak awithang leek awi amak ngai thlangkhqi ce anih ing phep kaw.
\v 9 Kumqui seetnaak ing a mingmih ce phep kawmsaw Bawipa amah ing amah a boeimang thaawmnaak a hai awhkawng hawi taak na awm kaw.
\v 10 Ak thlangciim khqing lakawh zoeksangnaak ingkaw ak cangnaak thlangkhqi boeih aham kawpoek kyi awmhlynaak khawnghi ce awm kaw. Nangmih a venawh kak kqawn law awi ce namik cangnaak a dawngawh, nangmih awm ce ak khuiawh thum lawt kawm uk ti.
\v 11 Ve ak awi ve kawlung khuiawh taak doena, Khawsa ing nangmih anik khynaak khqi ing ak tyng na nami awmnaak thai aham ingkaw nangmih ing naming cainaak ak nep soeih ce a soep sak thainaak aham ik-oeih nami sainaak hoei awh cangnaak ing nami saithainaak aham cykcah poepa unyng.
\v 12 Nangmih a Khawsa ingkaw Bawipa Jesu Khrih ang ming ce nangmih awh zoeksang na a awmnaak ham ingkaw nangmih awm amah awh ce zoeksang na nami awmnaak thai aham cykcah unyng.
\c 2
\s1 Thesalonika Khawawh Paul A Bibi
\p 
\v 1 Ni Bawipa Jesu Khrih a lawnaak ingkaw amah awh ningnih ning cun awh ce, koeinaakhqi,
\v 2 thlang pynoet ak awiphawngnaak aw, awikqawnnaak aw, capat mai aw kaimih a venawh kaw ak law amyihna, Bawipa a khawnghi pha law hawh hy tinawh kqawnnaak awi a awm awhtaw am nami lynaak aham kqawn law nyng.
\v 3 U ingawm nangmih koeh ni thai nak khqi seh, qaal na ak tho thlang ingkaw seetnaak ahamna ak awm lap hang na bi ak bi ak thlang ang dang law hlan dy taw, ce a khawnghi ce am pha law kaw.
\v 4 Khawsa tinawh khy aham ingkaw amah ce bawk aham, Khawsa a bawkim awh amah ingkaw amah ce hawih qu nawh Khawsa na amah ingkaw amah ak kqawn qu thlang ce qaal na tho kawmsaw zoeksang kawm uh.
\v 5 Nangmih a venawh ka awm awh vemyih ik-oeih akawng ka nik kqawn law peek khqi am nami sim nawh nu?
\v 6 A tym a khoek awh ang dang naak aham, anih a hu na tu na awm hyn hy tice sim uhyk ti.
\v 7 Tuh anaa amak ta thlangkhqi ing ang hyp na bibi hawh uhy; cawhkaw bi ak bikung ce khoe valh na a awm hlan dy bibi hun kaw.
\p 
\v 8 Cawhtaw anaa amak takhqi ce dang hawh kawm uh, cemyih thlangkhqi ce Bawipa Jesu ing boeimang soeih na a law awh am kha awhkaw hqi ing hqe boeih kaw.
\v 9 Anaa amak ta ing setan a bibinaak amyihna amak thym kawpoek kyi ik-oeih, hatnaak ingkaw ngaih kyinaak boeih ce haw na kawmsaw bibi kaw.
\p 
\v 10 Them amak leek soepkep ingkaw ak qeeng kawi thlangkhqi ce thai na kawm uh. Cemyih ak thlangkhqi ing awitak ce lungna nawh hulnaak huh aham amik thanaak a dawngawh qeeng kawm uh.
\v 11 Cedawngawh a mingmih ing qaai awi ce amik cangnaak aham Khawsa ing thlakthai ce tyih pehy.
\v 12 Awitak ce cangnaak kaana themche sainaak awh ak zeel thlangkhqi boeih thawlh sak na a awm thainaak aham cemyihna awm kaw.
\s1 Ak Cak Na Dyi Uh
\p 
\v 13 Bawipa ing a lungnaak koeinaakhqi, Myihla ciimsaknaak ingkaw awitak cangnaak ak caming hul aham ak cyk ca awhkawng Khawsa ing anik tyk khqi hawh a dawngawh, nangmih aham Khawsa venawh zeelawi ka mik kqawn poepa aham awm hy.
\v 14 Ni Bawipa Jesu Khrih a boeimangnaak awh nami paa naak thai aham kaimih ak awithang leek kqawnnaak ing nangmih ce nik khy khqi hy.
\v 15 Cedawngawh koeinaakhqi, ak cak na dyi unawh kaimih ing awi ing aw hui am lai ing aw ca ing aw ka mik kqawn law patoe ce ak cakna tu lah uh.
\v 16 Ni Bawipa Jesu Khrih amah qoe ing ningnih ani lungnaak khqi nawh am qeennaak ing kumqui thaawmnaak ingkaw ngaih-uunaak leek anik pekung Pa Khawsa ing,
\v 17 namik kawlung ce tha pe seitaw bi sainaak ingkaw awih kqawnnaak boeih awh tha ni awm sak khqi seh.
\c 3
\s1 Kaimih Ham Cykcah Uh
\p 
\v 1 A hukhit awhtaw koeinaakhqi, nangmih a venawh ka mik kqawn amyihna, Bawipa ak awithang ve kqihchahnaak ing ang tawnna a thangnaak aham kaimih aham cykcah lah uh.
\v 2 Thlang boeih cangnaak ama taak a dawngawh, thlakthawlh ingkaw thlakche a kut khuiawh kawng ka mi loetnaak aham cykcah lah uh.
\v 3 Cehlai Bawipa taw ypawm nawh anih ing nangmih ce tha ni awm sak khqi kawmsaw thlang amak leek a kut khui awhkawng ni loet sak khqi bit kaw.
\v 4 Kaimih ing ka mik kqawn law ce nami sai hawh amyihna sai poe kawm uk ti, tinawh Bawipa ak caming ka ming ngaih yp hy.
\v 5 Bawipa ing nangmih ak kawlung ce Khawsa lungnaak ingkaw Khrih ang yh thainaak benna sawi law seh.
\s1 Timote Ak Thapek Awi
\p 
\v 6 Koeinaakhqi, kaimih ing ka ni cawngpyi khqi amyihna am awm nawh tha ak dam thlangkhqi ce nami qei aham Bawipa Jesu Khrih ang ming ing awi ni pek khqi nyng.
\v 7 Ikawmyihna kaimih a awm a ih nami oet hly tice na mimah ing sim hawh uhyk ti. Nangmih a venawh ka mi awm awh ka mik tha am dam qoe qoe hy,
\v 8 a phu a peek kaana u a mih a buh awm a zoe na am ai unyng. U awm phyihqih am ka mi peeknaak aham khawmthan khawdai ak tlo tlo na bibi unyng.
\v 9 Saithainaak am kami taak awh am nawh nangmih a oet kawi na ka mi awmnaak aham cemyihna bi ce bi unyng.
\v 10 Nangmih a venawh ka mi awm awh vawhkaw awi ve ni pek khqi nyng: “Bi amak bi taw, a ai na awm koeh ai seh,” a tive.
\v 11 Nangmih ak khuiawh thlang vang taw amik tha dam hy ti za nyng. Bibi kaana; Bi ak bi na ak sa qukhqi awm awm hy tinawh za nyng.
\v 12 Cemyih thlangkhqi ce bibi unawh a mimah ak phoen ami khuut aham Bawipa Jesu Khrih ak caming awi pe nyng.
\p 
\v 13 Koeinaakhqi, nangmih ingtaw ak thym bi sai ve koeh ngak law qoe qoe uh.
\v 14 Vawhkaw ca ing ka ni yyn law khqi awi ve amak ngai ak thlang a awm awhtaw, anih ce hat law uh. Ak chahnaak aham koeh pawlneng law uh.
\v 15 Cehlai qaal a myih aih na taw koeh poek law uh, koeinaa amyihna anih ce cuk am kik law uh.
\v 16 Ngaihqepnaak ak pekung Bawipa amah qoe qoe ing nangmih ce a hun a hoei awh ityk awh awm ngaihqepnaak ni pek khqi seh. Nangmih boeih a venawh Bawipa taw awm seh.
\v 17 Kai, Paul ing ve kut tlaihnaak ca ve kamah a kut qoe qoe ing qee law nyng, ca ka pat khqi boeih ak khuiawh ve ve a lawhanaak na awm hy. Vemyihna ca ni qee law pek khqi nyng.
\v 18 Nami Bawipa Jesu Khrih am qeennaak nangmih boeih ak khanawh awm seh. 
